query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('scifi')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('a-song-of-ice-and-fire',
'aliens',
'comics',
'marvel-cinematic-universe',
'novel',
'star-trek-tng',
'the-lord-of-the-rings');
